---
title: Sweet and Sticky Chicken Udon Noodles with Bell Pepper and Sugar Snap Peas
description: This delicious Sweet and Sticky Chicken Udon Noodles has been expertly designed by our chefs as a lighter option to help with a balanced lifestyle.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R24_W33_UK_G2996-18187-7_Mainhigh-934fce46.jpg
